## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data and reports up to October 2023. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, including potential biases in reporting and the evolving nature of media trust dynamics. Additionally, the complexity of individual beliefs and media consumption habits means that generalizations may not apply to all Republicans.